    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q REMASTERED, the masterpiece of physics puzzles, is now available on Steam with the newly released Korean language support!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152610/extras/f9d8bc8293eeddcd68f4606a3a29adaf.avif?t=1729881236\" width=616 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game &quot;Q&quot; is a simple puzzle game that anyone can enjoy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can freely draw lines and shapes on the screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The drawn object will fall down due to gravity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will use the object to solve more than 1200 missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The solution is entirely up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152610/extras/c402f4be6f0708b2bae76a27a2245f1b.poster.avif?t=1729881236\" width=640 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152610/extras/c402f4be6f0708b2bae76a27a2245f1b.webm?t=1729881236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152610/extras/c402f4be6f0708b2bae76a27a2245f1b.mp4?t=1729881236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you get the ball out of the cup?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you hit the ball to the wall?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you know what the hell I'm talking about?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are confident, by all means take up the challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, the long-awaited new mode for the Steam version is the &quot;IQ TEST&quot; new mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How about your Q &quot;IQ&quot;?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new mode, IQ TEST, is now available to visualize your Q&quot;IQ&quot; value!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be diagnosed with an IQ number and a graph analyzing you through a dedicated stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152610/extras/7bbfdb088d6eb951f31ac9dece675d03.poster.avif?t=1729881236\" width=640 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152610/extras/7bbfdb088d6eb951f31ac9dece675d03.webm?t=1729881236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152610/extras/7bbfdb088d6eb951f31ac9dece675d03.mp4?t=1729881236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
